{
  "description": "This image captures a powerful waterfall cascading down a steep, rocky cliff face. The foreground is dominated by large, wet boulders and a small pool of water, hinting at the forceful energy of the water. The waterfall itself is a frothy white stream, creating a visible mist as it plunges downwards. The surrounding cliffs are sheer and dark, with patches of greenery clinging to the rock. The sky is overcast, creating a moody and dramatic atmosphere. The composition emphasizes the scale and power of nature, with the boulders providing a sense of immediacy and the waterfall towering above.",
